These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, mystery, scientific
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, swisher, vegafina
1. the person watching adventure movies is the swisher-smoker##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
4. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | scientific | mystery    |
| Cigar     | swisher    | vegafina       | old-henry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, pilot
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, bird
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the pilot is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left or far right##3
4. the librarian is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | pilot | fisherman | librarian  |
| Pet   | goldfish  | goat  | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, paramedic, videographer
3 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, go
1. the person playing canasta is on the far left or far right##3
2. the accountant is on the far right##1
3. the paramedic is the person playing go##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | videographer | paramedic | accountant |
| Game   | backgammon        | go    | canasta        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, iris, amaryllis
3 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, mouse
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
3. the owner of the fish is between the person who growsamaryllis and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Flower   | amaryllis | iris | marigold |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | fish    | mouse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, soul
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, subway, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the fan of classical##1
4. the fan of classical is between the fan of punk and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | punk | classical | soul |
| Transport     | subway   | ship   | taxi   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
City: boston, san-francisco, london
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, engineer, lawyer
1. the lawyer is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
4. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| City   | london | boston | san-francisco      |
| Job     | engineer  | lawyer | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, rock, techno
House: tower, gothic-revival, cape-cod
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | techno    | funk       |
| House   | gothic-revival | cape-cod | tower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, thai, indian
There 3 different types of food: grapes, orange, pomegranate
1. the indonesian is the person eating grapes##1
2. the person eating orange is in the middle##1
3. the indian is on the left of the thai##1
4. the thai is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Nationality   | indian        | thai  | indonesian   |
| Food       | pomegranate | orange | grapes |

