.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-9::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, scooter
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, r&b, techno
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3    |
| Transport           | quad-bike | ship | scooter |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | disco | r&b     |

