.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, water
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, r&b, salsa
1. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
2. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite    | water      |
| Music-Genre   | r&b       | disco | salsa |

