.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, water
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, april, march
1. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking tea##2
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage      | tea    | water    | sprite  |
| Birthday   | april | july | march |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, freelancer, pilot
3 different pets are kept: cat, horse, rabbit
1. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3
2. the pilot is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the cat##2
4. the owner of the cat is the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | bartender | pilot | freelancer |
| Pet           | horse    | rabbit    | cat       |

