.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-14::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, snowmobile, train
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, snowboarding, swimming
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
3. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Transport   | train    | airplane   | snowmobile |
| Sport   | snowboarding | swimming | parkour |

