.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-19::.
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, corn
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea, cola
1. the person eating cabbage is the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
3. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |
