.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, rowing
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | hot-chocolate | 7up         |
| Sport   | rowing | baseball  | badminton |

 